The '''Medx homunculi''' was an unsettling little creature, looking uncannily like a bony [[Human/Legends|Human]] scaled down to thirty centimeters in height.

They inhabited the wispy treetops of [[Gravlex Med/Legends|Gravlex Med]] and&mdash;while not sentient&mdash;were quite clever for animals. The striking resemblance between these chittering creatures and the [[Species/Legends|species]] that ruled the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] was a private joke among the [[Anx/Legends|Anx]].

